My new blog that runs off of my turbine engine I am working on.

You just post (or put) a block of text to it and it figures out the subclass of PostType that you are trying to make.

I will write more here if/when I get this thing more fully finished.

If you want to play, you can do:

> irb -r blog.rb
> thin -R config.ru start

Sinatra is sooooo ruby like, it's awesome.